<!--======= SERVICE SECTION =========-->
<section id="services" class="sectoion-100px services light-gray-bg">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="tittle">
			<h4>WHY ARE WE HERE?</h4>
			<p><span>LGBT</span>, who occupy approximately 11% of the Australian population, has the lowest participation in sports compared to other communities as a result of Homophobia</p>
			<p>A research based in Australia suggests that 50% of the LGBT community believe that they are 'not accepted' by the sports culture and community</p>
		</div>
<div class="tittle">
	<h4>services that we provide</h4>
</div>
<ul class="row">
<li class="col-md-4">
